{"tid":1627191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"這個夏天，人手一頂","createTime":"2019-10-05T14:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:54:37.000Z","uid":220767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a18aa35279b1e970aef67dcbbab24a2d3776b5","tid":1627191,"uid":220767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:54:37.000Z","msg":"女人一白遮三醜，踏入十月香港的紫外線仍然高企。<br />\n陽光除咗會令皮膚變黑仲會加速衰老。<br />\n普通嘅帽子已經唔能夠全面咁照顧我貪靚嘅需要。<br />\n我需要一頂能夠遮住耳仔、頸、面頰嘅遮陽帽。<br />\n見到周星馳拍戲嗰陣經常帶着呢款帽即刻心心眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYAAw7B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYAAw7B.jpg&h=a260e869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YT7nWzh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYT7nWzh.jpg&h=4a88d023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上淘寶幾十蚊仲有升級版<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMeQ5qE.png是\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMeQ5qE.png%E6%98%AF&h=03be0cb9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}